        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Military Aviation Training Safeguard Act</b></p> <p>This bill allows military aircraft operating outside of designated Department of Defense airspace while flying in wilderness areas in mountainous regions to deviate from service level requirements if necessary to maintain safety of flight. </p>]]></text>
